Tarsheva Longreach is a knowledgeable human planewalker, the narrator of The Planewalker's Handbook and the Negative Energy Plane chapter in The Inner Planes.
Illustration: The Planewalker's Handbook, page 5
Tarsheva's recommendations: The Planewalker's Handbook, page 9, 10, 12, 15, 16, 17, 18, 20, 21, 22, 23, 24, 25, 27, 28, 29, 31, 32, 33
Quotes: The Planewalker's Handbook, 4, 5, 6, 137; The Inner Planes, page 64, 68; Tales From the Infinite Staircase, page 84; The Great Modron March page 124; Dead Gods, page 6
Mentions: A Guide to the Ethereal Plane, page 4